*Master model selection and simplification in R: a two-day intensive
workshop*

https://prstats.org/course/model-selection-and-model-simplification-msms06/

Are you ready to elevate your statistical modelling skills? Join PR Stats?
hands-on, two-day workshop ?Model Selection and Model Simplification
(MSMS06)? designed for researchers who wish to make robust, reproducible
decisions when choosing and refining models.

*What you will learn*

   -

   How to compare and evaluate statistical models using information
   criteria (AIC, AICc, BIC) and cross-validation.
   -

   Techniques for regularisation, variable selection and avoiding
   overfitting through model-averaging and mixed-effects model selection.
   -

   Best practices for transparent, theory-driven analysis ? moving beyond
   ?which variables give the lowest p-value? towards scientifically sound
   model workflows.

*Why this course matters*
Statistical models are only as useful as the decisions behind them.
Choosing a model that fits the data perfectly but fails to generalise, or
simplifying without justification, undermines credibility and research
impact. This course gives you the methodological foundation and practical
skills to select and simplify models with confidence.

*Format & practicalities*

   -

   Duration: Two days (each day 6 hours) in a live-online format.
   -

   Fully hands-on: you will work with real datasets in R, guided
   step-by-step and supported with instructor resources.
   -

   Includes code scripts, demonstrations of comparative modelling
   workflows, and peer discussion of model strategy.

*Who should attend*
Researchers, postdocs, data analysts, and decision-scientists who already
use R for statistical modelling and wish to advance their practice in model
selection, comparison and simplification. Prior knowledge of linear models
and basic R is expected, but the focus is on applied model strategy rather
than mathematical theory.
------------------------------

Make smarter modelling decisions, strengthen your inference workflow, and
enhance the reproducibility of your analyses. Sign up now and secure your
place for this advanced modelling workshop.

For registration details and schedule, visit the PR Stats website.

https://prstats.org/course/model-selection-and-model-simplification-msms06/

